# 📦 Changelog

All notable changes to **FarminAI Assistant** will be documented in this file.

This project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/).

---

## [1.0.0] - 2025-07-23

### 🎉 Initial Release

- ✅ Streamlit app structure created
- ✅ Sidebar navigation with:
  - Home
  - Disease Detection
    - Poultry
    - Cow
    - Crop
  - Farm Record Keeping
- ✅ Modularized code using `pages/` directory
- ✅ Added logo image and basic UI layout
- ✅ Set wide layout for full-width experience

---

